id: pm-8fvl
title: Harden recursive test-all detection for npx package specs
description: Reject linked test commands that invoke pm test-all via npx package-spec forms like pm-cli@latest.
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[6]: "area:test-command",code,"milestone:3",pm-cli,"priority:1",tests
created_at: "2026-03-05T00:01:19.931Z"
updated_at: "2026-03-05T00:16:36.548Z"
deadline: "2026-03-06T00:01:19.000Z"
author: cursor-maintainer
estimated_minutes: 75
acceptance_criteria: pm test --add rejects recursive test-all invocations launched through npx package specs such as pm-cli@latest; unit tests cover detection paths; sandboxed regression and coverage remain at 100 percent.
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  pm-k3zx,related,"2026-03-05T00:01:19.931Z",cursor-maintainer,null
comments[7]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-03-05T00:01:19.931Z",cursor-maintainer,Docs require recursive pm test-all entries to be rejected and package-spec launchers currently bypass validation.
  "2026-03-05T00:01:31.917Z",cursor-maintainer,"Planned changeset: update PRD/README wording to explicitly include npx package-spec recursive forms, then harden src/cli/commands/test.ts detection and add unit regression coverage."
  "2026-03-05T00:02:54.435Z",cursor-maintainer,"Docs-first update completed: PRD README and AGENTS now explicitly include package-spec launcher forms (for example npx pm-cli@latest --json test-all) in recursive test-all reject/skip requirements."
  "2026-03-05T00:03:35.199Z",cursor-maintainer,Implemented parser hardening in src/cli/commands/test.ts by normalizing package specifiers before pm-cli launcher matching; added unit regressions for npx pm-cli@latest and npx pm-cli@0.1.0 add-time rejection plus runtime skip coverage.
  "2026-03-05T00:05:16.901Z",cursor-maintainer,"Follow-up fix after initial coverage run: removed unreachable empty-specifier branch in normalizePackageSpecifier and added scoped package regression cases (npx @scope/pm-cli@latest recursive reject plus npx @scope non-pm passthrough) to restore 100% coverage."
  "2026-03-05T00:06:21.258Z",cursor-maintainer,"Coverage follow-up: added npx @scope/pm-cli recursive rejection case to exercise scoped package branch without explicit version suffix so branch coverage remains at 100 percent."
  "2026-03-05T00:16:32.203Z",cursor-maintainer,"Evidence: pm test pm-8fvl --run --timeout 2400 --json passed 2/2 linked tests (coverage + targeted test-command suite). pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 2400 --json totals items=1 linked_tests=2 passed=2 failed=0 skipped=0. pm test-all --status closed --timeout 2400 --json totals items=64 linked_tests=202 passed=57 failed=0 skipped=145. Coverage gate output reports 100% statements/branches/functions/lines."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-03-05T00:01:19.931Z",cursor-maintainer,Plan docs-first clarification then parser hardening in src/cli/commands/test.ts plus targeted unit regressions.
